The CardDatabase is responsible for holding the card and set maps.
The CardDatabaseManager is responsible for managing the global database singleton.
The CardDatabaseModel maps the cardList contained in the CardDatabase as a QAbstractListModel.
The CardDatabaseLoader is responsible for populating the card database from files on disk.
The CardDatabaseQuerier is responsible for querying the database and returning data.
